<p>“How likely is it that you would recommend our product to a friend or colleague?”</p>

<p>This question is the basis of Net Promoter Score, NPS, which you can use to quickly and easily find out what your customer think of your products and services.</p>

<p>This survey is based on a scale between 0-10, which is divided into three categories; Dectractors (0-6), Passives (7-8). and Promoters (9-10). 
The NPS score is result of subtracting the share of Detractors form the share of Promoters, providing a score ranging from -100 to 100.</p>
    
<p>Services included:</p>

<ul>
<li>Write and Send Messages</li>
<li>First Come, First Served</li>
<li>Send Messages with Attribute Filter</li>
</ul>
